						<p>I&#8217;m not saying that taste is in any way universal or even that MochiKit is what you should be using.  However, you said there are &#8220;things&#8221; you don&#8217;t like about it, but you only mentioned the (irrelevant) script loading.  You should report the other things you dislike.</p>
