							<cite>Comment by <a href='http://bob.pythonmac.org/' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Bob Ippolito</a> &#8212; <time datetime="2006-05-06T04:32:06+00:00">May 6, 2006 @ 4:32 am</time> <a href="#comment-1519">#</a> </cite>
